  "text": "Gabriel, Lizaso, and Quemada (2010) and [CITATION_1] . The experiment consisted in a complete randomized design with five fertiliser treatments and six replications. The plot size was 6 \u00c2 6 m 2 and the measurements, either at ground or remote level, were taken in the central 3 \u00c2 3 m 2 central square. Treatments consisted of various N fertiliser rates 0, 70, 120, 170 and 220 kg N ha",
